     "A tandem gene duplication followed by recruitment of a
     retrotransposon created the paralogous bucentaur gene (bcntp97) in the
     ancestral ruminant."
     Mol. Biol. Evol. 23:798-806(2006).
     PubMed=16384818; DOI=10.1093/molbev/msj088
[ 3] Wisniewski T.P., Tanzi C.L., Gindhart J.G.
